
**an intoxicating liquor which is formed by macerating or infusin the poppy heads in water and sweetening the smae with molasses it is drunk by fakirs and by some others on festival occasions**
**சொற்குவை - அகரமுதலித் திட்ட இயக்ககம்**
- -   அபினிச்சாராயம்
-


